<h2 class="sectionedit3"><a name="teaching_materials_and_grading" id="teaching_materials_and_grading">Teaching Materials and Grading</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
The curriculum will be taken from «Computers as Components: Principles of Embedded Computing System Design» by Marilyn Wolf.
</p>

<p>
The final grade is decided by:
</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Exercise 1 (10%)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Exercise 2 (20%)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Exercise 3 (20%)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Final exam (50%)</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
